' =============================================================================
' GTNH Platform — User Flow: Machine Operations & Energy
' 3 диаграммы: machine lifecycle, Energy/Recipe flow, multiblock formation
' =============================================================================

' ===========================================================================
' 1. Machine Lifecycle (Furnace/Macerator/Compressor)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml machine-lifecycle
title **Flow M1: Machine Lifecycle (20 Hz Tick)**

actor "SimulationCore\n(20 Hz Tick)" as Tick
participant "MachineSystem" as MachineSys
participant "RecipeManager" as RM
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "EntityStateStore" as ESS
participant "ECS Registry" as ECS

== Каждый тик 20 Гц ==

Tick -> MachineSys: tick(dt)
MachineSys -> ECS: view<MachineComponent, EnergyStorage, Position>()

note right #438D80
  Машины (single-block):
  furnace (36) - HEAT
  macerator (48) - HEAT
  steam_macerator (51) - STEAM
  steam_compressor (52) - STEAM
  alloy_smelter (60) - STEAM
  extractor (61) - STEAM
  mixer (62) - STEAM
end note

loop For each machine
    MachineSys -> MachineSys: Check has valid recipe assigned

    alt No recipe assigned
        MachineSys -> RM: FindRecipe(machine_id, input items)
        RM --> MachineSys: Recipe found / not found

        alt Recipe found
            MachineSys -> MachineSys: Assign recipe, calc duration
        else No recipe
            MachineSys -> MachineSys: Idle
        end
    end

    alt Recipe is running
        MachineSys -> PN: CheckEnergy(machine_id, recipe.energy_cost/tick)
        PN --> MachineSys: Energy available / not

        alt Energy available
            MachineSys -> MachineSys: Consume recipe.energy_cost
            MachineSys -> MachineSys: Advance recipe progress
            MachineSys -> PN: ConsumeEnergy(energy_cost)
        else No energy
            MachineSys -> MachineSys: Pause, keep progress
        end
    end

    alt Recipe complete
        MachineSys -> MachineSys: Consume input items
        MachineSys -> MachineSys: Produce output items
        MachineSys -> RM: GetNextRecipe
        RM --> MachineSys: Next recipe / none

        alt Next recipe exists
            MachineSys -> MachineSys: Start next recipe
        else No next recipe
            MachineSys -> MachineSys: Idle, wait for input
        end
    end

    MachineSys -> ESS: UpdateMachineState
    note right: Persists: energy.current, progress, inventory
end

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 2. Energy Flow (Generator -> Network -> Machine)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml machine-energy-flow
title **Flow M2: Energy Flow (Generator -> PipeNetwork -> Machine)**

actor "SimulationCore\n(20 Hz Tick)" as Tick
participant "GeneratorSystem" as GenSys
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "MachineSystem" as MachineSys
participant "ECS Registry" as ECS
participant "CreativeGeneratorSystem" as Creative

== Фаза 1: Генерация энергии ==

Tick -> GenSys: tick(dt)
GenSys -> ECS: view<MachineComponent, EnergyStorage>

note right #E67E22
  Источники энергии:
  heat_generator (46) - HEAT из топлива
  steam_solid_boiler (49) - STEAM из топлива
  steam_heat_boiler (50) - STEAM из HEAT
  creative_generator (63) - ELECTRICITY ∞
end note

loop For each generator
    GenSys -> GenSys: Check fuel in inventory
    GenSys -> Generator: Burn fuel, produce energy
    GenSys -> PN: DistributeEnergy(machine_id, produced)
end

Tick -> Creative: tick(dt)
Creative -> Creative: Produces unlimited ELECTRICITY
Creative -> PN: DistributeEnergy(creative_id, 1024 EU/t)

== Фаза 2: PipeNetwork распределение ==

Tick -> PN: tick(dt)
PN -> PN: BFS через pipe graph

note right #5899DA
  PipeNetwork:
  - Поиск подключённых машин (BFS)
  - Распределение энергии
  - Приоритет: ближайшие машины
  - Лимиты per pipe/tick
end note

loop For each energy source
    PN -> PN: BFS from source through pipes
    PN -> PN: Find connected consumers
    loop For each consumer
        PN -> PN: Calculate distribution %
        PN -> PN: Transfer energy (limited by pipe throughput)
    end
end

== Фаза 3: Потребление энергии ==

Tick -> MachineSys: tick(dt)
MachineSys -> MachineSys: For each running machine
MachineSys -> PN: RequestEnergy(machine_id, recipe_energy_cost)
PN --> MachineSys: Energy delivered / insufficient

alt Energy received
    MachineSys -> MachineSys: Advance recipe
else No energy
    MachineSys -> MachineSys: Pause
end

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 3. Multiblock formation
' ===========================================================================
@startuml machine-multiblock-formation
title **Flow M3: Multiblock Formation (3x3x3)**

actor "Игрок" as Player
participant "GameClient" as Client
participant "Gateway" as GW
participant "MessageRouter" as MR
participant "ChunkStore" as CS
participant "SimulationCore\n(ECS)" as Sim
participant "EntityStateStore" as ESS
participant "RecipeManager" as RM

Player -> Client: Ставит последний блок паттерна
Client -> GW: SetBlockAction(pos, block_id, CAS)
GW -> MR: Publish world.blocks.set
MR -> CS: SetBlock CAS
CS -> MR: Publish world.blocks.changed
MR -> Sim: onBlockChanged(pos, block_id, mb_id)

Sim -> Sim: Проверка: isPatternComplete(pos)

note right #9B59B6
  Multiblock detection:
  1. Получить все блоки вокруг pos
  2. Сравнить с зарегистрированными паттернами
  3. Если совпало -> MultiblockController
end note

alt Pattern match found
    Sim -> Sim: Create MultiblockController entity
    Sim -> Sim: Add ECS components:\nMachineComponent + EnergyStorage + Position
    Sim -> CS: RPC: SetBlockMeta для всех блоков\n(запись mb_id в meta-layer)
    Sim -> Sim: Register all blocks positions
    Sim -> ESS: Save multiblock state
    Sim -> MR: Publish sim.multiblock.created
    MR -> GW: Relay to all clients
    GW -> Client: BlockUpdate (multiblock visual)
    Client -> Player: Multiblock appears active

    Sim -> RM: Register multiblock recipes
    RM --> Sim: Recipes registered

else Pattern not complete
    Sim -> Sim: Single block only
    Sim -> CS: RPC: SetBlockMeta(none)
end

== Multiblock dissociation ==

Player -> Client: Ломает ключевой блок мультиблока
Client -> GW: BreakBlockAction(pos)
GW -> MR: Publish world.blocks.set (AIR)
MR -> Sim: onBlockChanged(pos, AIR)
Sim -> Sim: Check: isMultiblockAnchor(pos)

alt Anchor block broken
    Sim -> Sim: Destroy MultiblockController entity
    Sim -> Sim: Remove ECS components
    Sim -> CS: RPC: ClearBlockMeta для всех блоков
    Sim -> ESS: Remove multiblock state
    Sim -> MR: Publish sim.multiblock.destroyed
end

@enduml
